Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:31.85,OP11 Credits,,50,0,230,,Translation\N FUNimation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:32.51,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Working together, let's ride the giant waves{\i}
